These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-8-1::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: coffee, tea
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: sailing, snowboarding
2 different games are played: snooker, scrabble
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: february, june
1. the person who's birthday is in february is not to the right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##8
2. the person who's sport is snowboarding is somewhere to the left of the person playing snooker##5
3. the person drinking coffee is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |
| Beverage      | tea     | coffee      |
| Sport          | snowboarding | sailing    |
| Game         | scrabble   | snooker |
| Birthday   | february  | june      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-8-2::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, iced-tea
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: cain, montecristo
There are 2 different nationalities: malaysian, american
City: london, edinburgh
1. the person drinking iced-tea is on the far right##1
2. the cain-smoker is somewhere to the left of the malaysian##5
3. the american is not to the right of the malaysian##8
4. the person traveling to london is not the montecristo-smoker##6

.:: Answer ::.
|             |         1          |      2      |
| Beverage    | almond-milk        | iced-tea    |
| Cigar       | cain         | montecristo |
| Nationality         | american | malaysian   |
| City   | london               | edinburgh  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-8-3::.
House: ranch-style, gothic-revival
City: berlin, miami
There are 2 different favourite colors: blue, pink
2 different pets are kept: cat, ferret
1. the person who likes blue is in an odd position##4
2. the person who likes pink is not to the right of the owner of the ferret##8
3. the person traveling to berlin is somewhere to the left of the gothic-revival house##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |
| House   | ranch-style       | gothic-revival |
| City   | berlin       | miami    |
| Color   | blue | pink |
| Pet           | cat        | ferret   |

