.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-8-4::.
2 different pets are kept: lizard, cat
There are 2 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, tea
There are 2 different nationalities: german, polish
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: october, november
1. the german is somewhere to the right of the person drinking tea##5
2. the owner of the lizard is not to the left of the person who's birthday is in november##8
3. the person who's birthday is in november is on the left of the owner of the lizard##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |
| Pet         | cat | lizard  |
| Beverage           | tea  | almond-milk |
| Nationality   | polish | german   |
| Birthday     | november   | october |

