.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-8-10::.
There 2 different types of food: cabbage, lettuce
There are 2 different nationalities: pakistani, argentine
2 different games are played: backgammon, go
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: tennis, cycling
1. the person eating cabbage is not to the left of the argentine##8
2. the person who's sport is tennis is the person who's sport is tennis##1
3. the person eating lettuce is somewhere to the right of the person playing backgammon##5
4. the person who's sport is tennis is not to the right of the person who's sport is cycling##8
5. the person who's sport is cycling is not to the left of the person eating lettuce##8

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |         2          |
| Food        | cabbage | lettuce            |
| Nationality       | argentine | pakistani              |
| Game         | backgammon  | go |
| Sport   | tennis     | cycling         |

