.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-8-12::.
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: house, classical
House: modern, cape-cod
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: animation, mystery
The people have 2 different hobbies: camping, collecting
1. the person watching mystery movies is not to the right of the person who's hobby is camping##8
2. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the left or right of the fan of classical##3
3. the person watching mystery movies is on the right of the person watching animation movies##1
4. the cape-cod house is on the right of the person who's hobby is collecting##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |
| Music-Genre      | house      | classical  |
| House          | modern   | cape-cod    |
| Movie-Genre   | animation | mystery |
| Hobby           | collecting       | camping     |

