3. the person driving the scooter is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |    2    |
| Flower          | balloon-flower         | azalea    |
| Music-Genre           | techno | reggae   |
| Cigar   | bongani   | cain    |
| Transport     | boat         | scooter |

 